        <Parent_String>vegetable black [300264725], carbon black [300013138], organic black pigment [300013136], black pigment [300013135], pigment by color [300013134], pigments [300013109], colorant (material) [300013026], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
